{"tid":2296618,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唐代墩古城考古驚現羅馬式浴場遺址","createTime":"2020-11-22T15:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T05:53:32.000Z","uid":226955,"like":90,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"497980ea58b5fce621d75b82d729f23b19b908e6","tid":2296618,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:23:43.000Z","msg":"Source: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/新疆絲路古城發現羅馬式浴場遺址-244092?fbclid=IwAR1QiZSvaXMkQWPXswLR_595l9xu3bZBOxvvDamvro_wiz09dBqER9_bSck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%B5%B2%E8%B7%AF%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E7%BE%85%E9%A6%AC%E5%BC%8F%E6%B5%B4%E5%A0%B4%E9%81%BA%E5%9D%80-244092%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1QiZSvaXMkQWPXswLR_595l9xu3bZBOxvvDamvro_wiz09dBqER9_bSck&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT4%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=f06239aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/新疆絲路古城發現羅馬式浴場遺址-244092?fbclid=IwAR1QiZSvaXMkQWPXswLR_595l9xu3bZBOxvvDamvro_wiz09dBqER9_bSck</a><br />\n<br />\n新疆絲路古城發現羅馬式浴場遺址<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGSuZPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGSuZPM.jpg&h=375234e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在「絲綢之路」必經之地新疆昌吉州奇台縣唐朝墩古城，新疆文物考古研究所與中國人民大學的考古人員2018年開始挖掘後，於東北部發現一排排磚砌通道和排水溝。經過近3年的發掘和研究，考古人員近日確定，該處是一個建於過千年前高昌回鶻時期(即唐宋時期)的公共浴場，形制布局、建築等方面都具有濃郁的羅馬風格，全國罕見，而牆面裝飾彩繪及各類出土物件卻極具中原和本地特色，反映東西方建築和技藝在絲綢之路上的交融與創新。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoXOvWw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoXOvWw.jpg&h=1361d5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n考古人員表示，浴場面積約300平方米，為半地穴式結構，下層位於地底，為煙道和供熱空間，用於維持浴場上層空間的溫度；上層位於地面，是浴場使用、活動空間。這種利用下層磚砌支撐柱為支架，分成上下兩個封閉空間的建築方式，在古羅馬時期《建築十書》中稱為「挑空式地板」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXKECBG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXKECBG.jpg&h=616361dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n考古人員還介紹，浴場分為大堂、工作區和洗浴區三大區域，設有冷水室、溫水室、熱水室、更衣室，甚至可能有桑拿室、蒸氣室。西北角有一口直徑超過2米、深約10米的大井，建於高台之上，相信是浴場水源。<br />\n<br />\n考古人員指出，浴場除了能滿足百姓日常清潔的需要，還能供往來旅人沐浴休息，並可見當時的當地人熱愛洗浴。此外，高昌回鶻時期，摩尼教和佛教盛行，而洗浴往往與宗教活動息息相關，故浴場也可能與宗教活動有一定關聯。考古人員又提到，浴場自14世紀蒙元時期逐漸廢棄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLMr13t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLMr13t.jpg&h=7d18dac0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56e9c0ab4ab9a8ea8c729768a5f62514b08c5c9e","tid":2296618,"uid":226955,"like":225,"dislike":1,"score":224,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"羅馬帝國也是中國不可分割的一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c350d92533f4a29a2aa9060ea321b95430ea1740","tid":2296618,"uid":231583,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd94b4f80563048ab88bce7daa5effed7fd08cd5","tid":2296618,"uid":54373,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:26:40.000Z","msg":"真係有高昌迷宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6abe0d61ca970561acde8a120e1166215668315","tid":2296618,"uid":165336,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"支那趕唔切係記者黎之前殺哂d學者再炸撚左個遺跡？<br />\n點可以俾D證明果個地方曾經唔係屬於支那既古蹟/文物出土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係搵到文明可以高價拍賣回返D血？"},{"pid":"1e6cc1f4a7338fa1e42f7566427af366536e6f61","tid":2296618,"uid":169195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c350d92533f4a29a2aa9060ea321b95430ea1740","tid":2296618,"uid":231583,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"quote":{"pid":"56e9c0ab4ab9a8ea8c729768a5f62514b08c5c9e","tid":2296618,"uid":226955,"like":225,"dislike":1,"score":224,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"羅馬帝國也是中國不可分割的一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci